title: Calendar app on phone not showing calendar subscription feeds
content: I have subscribed to 2 email URL subscription feeds it shows on my calendar for computer but not my phone calendar app. I need help in order to see this. I have 6 email accounts that i go back and forth with it. The app on my home page of my phone should show all calendar reminders and events but it doesn't & it doesn't show the URL subscription feeds. It only shows events i put on the phone calendar.
